</div></div><p itemprop="description">衣服采用透明塑料袋包装 。 <br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb7530299dc47608.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">包装背面印有授权信息，由上海三枪生产。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb75302b20717662.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">拿出来，平铺如下所示。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb75308a517f4216.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">吊牌价218元超级贵，双十一只要39块，还要付给迪士尼钱，加上原料、人工、物流，我好奇三枪能赚多少。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb75302be82d1082.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">先来看衣服。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb7530c21ac06122.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">衣服采用圆领，领口有包边处理。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb753182668c5369.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/35468/" data-brandid="35468" target="_blank">闪电</a>麦昆，应该男孩子们都知道吧，我儿子小时候特别喜欢看，翻来覆去看都不会厌，</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgom8n/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="三枪迪士尼汽车总动员儿童内衣套装" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb7530de2f1d8928.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">袖子上印有车子、<a c